mptoms together?","dimension":5,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.018602,0.058813,0.087767,0.10327,0.107,0.10741,0.10297,0.09966,0.095873,0.093344,0.077553,0.047735],"unified_progress":[0.036036,0.070009,0.082427,0.098445,0.096469,0.094841,0.098507,0.093652,0.090553,0.094432,0.080328,0.064301]},{"section":14,"text":"Malignancy comes to mind, especially since it can cause pain, doesn't respond well to antibiotics, and can erode bone.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.024659,0.042263,0.057399,0.071132,0.083165,0.093902,0.10406,0.10785,0.1134,0.12146,0.10957,0.071144],"unified_progress":[0.0347,0.057365,0.07416,0.083762,0.093795,0.10309,0.10142,0.10181,0.099414,0.09729,0.084791,0.068404]},{"section":15,"text":"But wait, let's not jump to conclusions too quickly.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.1078,0.086375,0.080828,0.073285,0.074849,0.077931,0.081279,0.091015,0.082592,0.057624,0.061386,0.12503],"unified_progress":[0.20155,0.076125,0.06383,0.064336,0.073294,0.073798,0.096499,0.08264,0.079689,0.064506,0.060251,0.063483]},{"section":16,"text":"Let's consider other possibilities.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.11674,0.10539,0.093914,0.078059,0.077691,0.078472,0.078339,0.088999,0.082321,0.054773,0.053869,0.09143],"unified_progress":[0.18271,0.060888,0.23453,0.079461,0.057418,0.056156,0.05612,0.064654,0.063287,0.052482,0.047464,0.044835]},{"section":17,"text":"Could it be malignant otitis externa?","dimension":4,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.031069,0.055529,0.074453,0.090458,0.097131,0.10421,0.11049,0.11015,0.10892,0.10479,0.073936,0.038857],"unified_progress":[0.041633,0.0785,0.080335,0.10522,0.11126,0.10196,0.099857,0.098275,0.091042,0.081861,0.065635,0.044413]},{"section":18,"text":"That's a possibility, but it's rare and usually affects people with weakened immune systems.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.029393,0.047792,0.061144,0.073509,0.08547,0.09825,0.10968,0.11669,0.12282,0.12114,0.089542,0.044579],"unified_progress":[0.038979,0.064445,0.082103,0.091065,0.099713,0.10294,0.10133,0.10167,0.0965,0.093367,0.075286,0.052596]},{"section":19,"text":"Our patient does have diabetes, which fits, but let's keep thinking.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.023153,0.039608,0.054605,0.067094,0.079085,0.094263,0.10861,0.12406,0.13393,0.13125,0.097619,0.046729],"unified_progress":[0.035727,0.060293,0.074594,0.083656,0.093641,0.095714,0.10001,0.10389,0.10225,0.1076,0.085991,0.056641]},{"section":20,"text":"Chronic otitis media could cause some similar symptoms, but it's less likely to cause such severe bony changes or facial nerve problems.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.020989,0.031932,0.042846,0.05405,0.06662,0.081517,0.098083,0.11165,0.12517,0.13979,0.13672,0.090645],"unified_progress":[0.033802,0.052496,0.067766,0.0777,0.08864,0.098433,0.10047,0.10535,0.10581,0.10622,0.094523,0.068796]},{"section":21,"text":"Hmm, maybe it's not that either.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.008983,0.026212,0.041472,0.055057,0.069892,0.090068,0.11196,0.13735,0.15546,0.15427,0.10752,0.04174],"unified_progress":[0.023256,0.051867,0.069128,0.079107,0.091621,0.094655,0.10166,0.10914,0.10912,0.11816,0.09606,0.056224]},{"section":22,"text":"Oh, what about malignant otitis externa caused by Pseudomonas aeruginosa?","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.013018,0.029072,0.044434,0.061083,0.078222,0.097772,0.11724,0.13012,0.14087,0.14584,0.10189,0.040433],"unified_progress":[0.02446,0.05302,0.072854,0.087753,0.096205,0.10791,0.10708,0.1095,0.105,0.10174,0.081361,0.053115]},{"section":23,"text":"That's known for being aggressive and causing bone erosion.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.01974,0.036182,0.047566,0.059875,0.073786,0